<span id="freeTextContainer16082791153901942862">Romancing Melody is the 3rd book in the Crossing Series by Carrie Dawes. We are briefly introduced to Melody in Ryan&apos;s Crossing, the 2nd book in the series. Melody is a young wife of a military man living at Fort Bragg, NC. Life as a military wife is not as she had expected. My breath was taken away several times as Melody journeyed through her husband being deployed when their baby was young. Tragedy strikes and she is faced with making some tough decisions. She finds comfort in places she leas</span>
  <span id="freeText16082791153901942862" style="display:none">Romancing Melody is the 3rd book in the Crossing Series by Carrie Dawes. We are briefly introduced to Melody in Ryan's Crossing, the 2nd book in the series. Melody is a young wife of a military man living at Fort Bragg, NC. Life as a military wife is not as she had expected. My breath was taken away several times as Melody journeyed through her husband being deployed when their baby was young. Tragedy strikes and she is faced with making some tough decisions. She finds comfort in places she least expected to. Melodys heartache and transformation and transformation are nothing less than miraculous. Gods timing is always perfect even though we may not see it at the time. 'For I know the plans I have for you, declares the Lord, plans for welfare[a] and not for evil, to give you a future and a hope.' Jer 29:11 I saw this truth through out the story. <br />I would highly recommend this book be added to your library. I was had a hard time putting it down. <br />I was provided this book by the author in exchange for my honest review.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="16082791153901942862" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

