        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer556761472" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12044920238298428760">Romancing Melody is a heartwarming story that draws you into the lives of a loving couple who question their faith when tragedy strikes. The characters are real and full of emotions we all share. You laugh with them, cry with them, and feel their pain. But, the characters also learn to trust God in the midst of their questions and turn to His Word for answers. Carrie has written a wonderful story that helps her readers relate to the characters in the book and apply God&apos;s love to their own lives.</span>
  <span id="freeText12044920238298428760" style="display:none">Romancing Melody is a heartwarming story that draws you into the lives of a loving couple who question their faith when tragedy strikes. The characters are real and full of emotions we all share. You laugh with them, cry with them, and feel their pain. But, the characters also learn to trust God in the midst of their questions and turn to His Word for answers. Carrie has written a wonderful story that helps her readers relate to the characters in the book and apply God's love to their own lives. I would highly recommend it to others!</span>
